@startuml
title 基于GitHub的实验管理平台--选择课程用例的顺序图

actor "教师" as Teacher1 at left
participant "系统\n(控制层)" as SystemController2 #lightblue 
database "数据库服务类" as DatabaseService3 

Teacher1 ->>SystemController2 :发起评分请求  
activate SystemController2   
    SystemController2->DatabaseService3:查询本学期当前教师所教授的课程    
        activate DatabaseService3        
            return返回课程信息       
        deactivate DatabaseService3     
return返回课程信息  

deactivate SystemController2   

note over Teacher1,SystemController2#right\ntext-align:center \n<font color=red><b>(循环开始)</b></font>\nnote bottom    

loop loop [for each student]      
   note right of Teacher1:text-align:left <u>*步骤说明*</u>:     
    
